---
import ThemeLayout from '../layouts/ThemeLayout.astro';
---
<ThemeLayout page="services" heading="B2C Development Services">

  <section class="inner-page padd-section">
    <div class="container">

      <div class="row align-items-center mb-5" data-aos="fade-up">
        <div class="col-md-2 col-sm-12 text-center mb-4 mb-md-0">
          <div class="svc-hero-icon">
            <i class="fa fa-shopping-cart"></i>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-10">
          <h3>Business-to-Consumer Development</h3>
          <p>Rayinfos Technologies is a leading player in B2C development, providing efficient programs that help enterprise growth, improved efficiency and the ability to compete on a global scale. Our B2C sites function across PHP, ASP.NET, XML, WebLogic and JavaScript platforms.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-globe"></i></div>
            <h5>Multi-platform Support</h5>
            <p>B2C sites that function across PHP, ASP.NET, XML, WebLogic and JavaScript, ensuring broad compatibility with modern technologies.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-refresh"></i></div>
            <h5>Workflow Automation</h5>
            <p>Implementation and automation of business workflows to reduce manual effort and improve the efficiency of your operations.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-file-text-o"></i></div>
            <h5>Content Management</h5>
            <p>Document and content management system integration, along with hosting services for websites to keep your content fresh and accessible.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-laptop"></i></div>
            <h5>B2C Web Portals</h5>
            <p>Feature-rich B2C portals incorporating individualised desktops, identity management and the latest querying tools for your customers.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-bar-chart"></i></div>
            <h5>Campaign Management</h5>
            <p>Excellent implementation and design of online advertising, marketing and promotional campaigns to increase brand awareness.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-check-circle"></i></div>
            <h5>Data Standards</h5>
            <p>Standardisation of incoming data using up-to-date modern technologies, ensuring proficiency across third-generation systems.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</ThemeLayout>
